    "description": "“佣兵传说2 赤诚银鹫”是一款战棋角色扮演游戏，在游戏中你要与银鹫佣兵队的队长克劳德和他的队员一起，在多达32个关卡中进行战斗。<br><br>【关于游戏】<br>・在俯视角的战斗地图上指挥你的部队，并带领他们取得胜利！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142240/extras/9129b64efd5d16109eb0796be50b4b37.poster.avif?t=1727198639\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142240/extras/9129b64efd5d16109eb0796be50b4b37.webm?t=1727198639\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142240/extras/9129b64efd5d16109eb0796be50b4b37.mp4?t=1727198639\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>・单位的位置会影响战斗中行动的结果。无论位于敌人的前方、后方、侧面，或是比目标更高的地方，都会产生不同的行动效果。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142240/extras/2b0566f51703bd616a0ad7523140b191.poster.avif?t=1727198639\" width=600 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142240/extras/2b0566f51703bd616a0ad7523140b191.webm?t=1727198639\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142240/extras/2b0566f51703bd616a0ad7523140b191.mp4?t=1727198639\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>・花费技能点数（SP）进行转职！角色升级之后，将能够解锁中级和高级职业。每个职业都有自己的一套技能可以学习。<br>特殊职业只能通过特殊道具来解锁。<br>搭建属于你自己的团队吧！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142240/extras/006d8108fce6a8e56658bf46541c8aa3.poster.avif?t=1727198639\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142240/extras/006d8108fce6a8e56658bf46541c8aa3.webm?t=1727198639\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142240/extras/006d8108fce6a8e56658bf46541c8aa3.mp4?t=1727198639\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>・花费SP学习新技能！根据所选择的职业，角色能够学习治疗或增益盟友的技能，以及对敌人造成减益或状态异常的技能。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142240/extras/3cb89ce7cfd2366c2527cb7456c1e0c0.poster.avif?t=1727198639\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142240/extras/3cb89ce7cfd2366c2527cb7456c1e0c0.webm?t=1727198639\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142240/extras/3cb89ce7cfd2366c2527cb7456c1e0c0.mp4?t=1727198639\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>・额外难度的“EX关卡”能让最熟练的策略玩家也感到满意。<br><br>【故事背景】<br>大国稳定统治的时代结束后，西大陆因小国之间的领土争端而动荡不安。<br><br>位于大陆东部的王国，虽然面积不大，但以北面的雪谷与西面的岩石山脉为天然要塞，成为一个历史悠久的独立国家。<br><br>传说这个王室的祖先在遥远的神之时代，<br>以一介战士之姿被神选中，成为驱逐黑暗生物的伟大英雄。<br><br>但是，经历了长久的太平盛世，继承英雄血脉的王室，<br>也变得只遵循长幼之序和外在形式，选出平庸的君王。<br>现任国王萨鲁德也因其朴实的性格而深受民众爱戴，<br>但他是一位在政治上并没有太大建树的国王。<br><br>就这样，王国在平静中继续没落，<br>远离王都的土地上充斥着凶恶的盗贼和魔物…",
